faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T04:52:29.000Z","msg":"係嘅巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a98448b636dd3a683cc821173fefd7ea18239ea","tid":920269,"uid":199636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T05:00:19.000Z","msg":"就咁樣，我失去咗同佢成日玩、傾計嘅機會。不過唔緊要，因為嗰陣我仲未覺得鐘意佢，依家諗返起，或者係因為我覺得佢係人地女朋友，有依種意欲都唔夠膽表現出黎。我地最多都係得閒講兩句，之後就都係摸下頭咁啦，不過喺我眼中已經係好少嘅接觸，一直到中五......<br />\n<br />\n「嗚嗚嗚，我好鐘意你架，如果唔係因為琦卓，我就會同你一齊架！」當我沖緊涼嗰陣，竟然有個女仔衝入黎攬住我。我望真啲，講依句野嘅就係子喬。下一刻，我驚醒咗，原來淨係一場夢......雖然鬆咗一口氣，但心入面卻有一種失落嘅感覺。究竟我係咪真係鐘意佢？定係咁啱好發咗個咁嘅夢炸？ 我唔知，我真係好亂，但又唔夠膽同其他人講，細細個嘅我更覺得咁樣係做第三者，係唔好嘅，所有野都唔夠膽宣之出口。"},{"pid":"af2c92b942147fba143023d709d7fcabc8f9b341","tid":920269,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T06:01:49.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00389374b9763c0f8c4a066a98695a5d4c8da702","tid":920269,"uid":199636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af2c92b942147fba143023d709d7fcabc8f9b341","tid":920269,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T06:01:49.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T08:03:01.000Z","msg":"但係冇人睇真係好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65fd12b1d5d90c0e3ff68be10f4c218e79b85909","tid":920269,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00389374b9763c0f8c4a066a98695a5d4c8da702","tid":920269,"uid":199636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af2c92b942147fba143023d709d7fcabc8f9b341","tid":920269,"ui